---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Challa's Counsel | Credentials & Philosophy" 
  description="Discover the clinical training, therapeutic approach, and professional values of Challa's Counsel."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[50vh] flex items-center bg-canvas pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 w-full">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center reveal">
        <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary block mb-4">Biography</span>
        <h1 class="font-sans font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-ink leading-tight tracking-tight">
          Guided by clinical expertise, rooted in <span class="font-display italic font-normal text-secondary">compassionate alignment</span>.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-body leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto mt-6">
          A collaborative path to understanding the patterns that shape your life and making room for genuine growth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bio Split -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-canvas border-t border-border/40">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
      <div class="space-y-8 reveal-left">
        <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-card aspect-[4/5] bg-canvas-warm group">
          <img 
            src="/images/dr_niharika_portrait.png" 
            alt="Mr. Challa looking thoughtful in his office" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" 
          />
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card rounded-lg p-8 border border-border/50 shadow-card space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary">Education & Credentials</h3>
          <div class="space-y-5 text-sm text-body">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-ink mb-1">Licensure & Certifications</h4>
              <p class="leading-relaxed">Licensed Professional Counselor<br>Certified Career and Family Consultant</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-ink mb-1">Education</h4>
              <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-ink">Master's in Counselling & Psychotherapy</strong><br><strong class="text-ink">Bachelor's in Psychology</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-ink mb-1">Specializations</h4>
              <p class="leading-relaxed">Individual Counselling, Couples & Family Therapy, Career Guidance, Anxiety & Depression Support</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-body text-base md:text-lg leading-[1.8] reveal-right">
        <h2 class="font-sans font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-ink leading-tight">My Therapeutic Philosophy</h2>
        <p>Many of the clients I work with describe feeling like they are living two lives. On the outside, they look highly successful, capable, and organized. On the inside, they are running on fumes, fighting constant anxiety, or feeling disconnected from their loved ones.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-ink font-semibold">This stress is not a personal failure.</strong> Often, our coping mechanisms were once critical survival strategies. But eventually, these patterns begin to cost us our energy, health, and peace of mind.</p>
        <p>My role is to serve as a supportive guide and clinical partner. We combine deep, insight-oriented talk therapy with practical physiological grounding tools to help you build safety within yourself.</p>
        <blockquote class="text-center border-l-4 border-secondary pl-6 py-4 italic text-ink font-display text-lg md:text-xl bg-card rounded-r-md shadow-sm">
          "Therapy works best as a collaboration. You are the expert on your life. I bring clinical frameworks, trauma-informed tools, and a non-judgmental presence to help you move forward."
        </blockquote>
        <p>Whether we are parsing career stress, navigating the end of a relationship, or working through anxiety, we go at a pace that honors your nervous system.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-canvas border-t border-border/40">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 space-y-4 reveal">
        <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary">Practice Foundation</span>
        <h2 class="font-sans font-bold text-4xl text-ink leading-tight tracking-tight">My Core Therapeutic Values</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 stagger-children">
        <div class="bg-card rounded-lg p-8 border border-border/50 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300">
          <span class="text-lg font-bold text-secondary font-sans block mb-4">01</span>
          <h3 class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-ink mb-3">Non-Pathologizing Lens</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
            We examine your responses as logical, understandable adaptations to stress or trauma and work to expand your natural capacity for resilience.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card rounded-lg p-8 border border-border/50 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300">
          <span class="text-lg font-bold text-primary font-sans block mb-4">02</span>
          <h3 class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-ink mb-3">Intersectional & Systemic</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
            We explicitly acknowledge how societal expectations, systemic pressures, gender dynamics, and identity impact your emotional health.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card rounded-lg p-8 border border-border/50 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300">
          <span class="text-lg font-bold text-secondary font-sans block mb-4">03</span>
          <h3 class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-ink mb-3">HIPAA-Secure Safety</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
            All booking, communications, telehealth sessions, and medical records adhere strictly to state and federal medical privacy standards.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to Expect -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-canvas border-t border-border/40">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 space-y-4 reveal">
        <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary">First Steps</span>
        <h2 class="font-sans font-bold text-4xl text-ink leading-tight tracking-tight">What to expect in our first session</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 stagger-children">
        <div class="flex gap-6 p-8 bg-card rounded-lg border border-border/50 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm bg-canvas-warm text-ink flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">01</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-lg text-ink mb-2">15-Minute Discovery Call</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
              We chat via phone or secure video to discuss what brings you to therapy, answer any logistics questions, and ensure my clinical approach is the right fit.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-6 p-8 bg-card rounded-lg border border-border/50 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm bg-canvas-warm text-ink flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">02</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-lg text-ink mb-2">Clinical Intake Session (50 min)</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
              We explore your personal history, unpack current triggers, and collaboratively map out a customized treatment plan tailored to your lifestyle.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-6 p-8 bg-card rounded-lg border border-border/50 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm bg-canvas-warm text-ink flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">03</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-lg text-ink mb-2">Ongoing Checkpoints & Reviews</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
              Every few weeks, we evaluate your progress, review symptom reduction, adjust somatic grounding models, and adapt clinical tools as needed.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-canvas border-t border-border/40">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="bg-ink rounded-lg p-12 md:p-16 text-center text-white relative overflow-hidden shadow-card-hover group">
        <div class="absolute -top-20 -left-20 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-primary/10 blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-20 -right-20 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-secondary/10 blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-6">
          <h2 class="font-sans font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white leading-tight">
            Take the next step in your <span class="font-display italic font-normal text-secondary">healing journey</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
            Schedule a free 15-minute consultation to check our fit. No commitment required.
          </p>
          <div class="pt-4">
            <a 
              href="/book" 
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 rounded-md bg-white hover:bg-zinc-100 text-ink font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg active:scale-[0.98]"
            >
              Book Discovery Call
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 text-ink"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
